review_blob: Love this beer. Heavy green tea flavor, with pine IPA undertones. This is a strong beer at 10.1S% ABV.
beer_name: Baird / Ishii / Stone Japanese Green Tea IPA 10.1% (2015)

review_blob: This is a great summer beer, however, I dont think it truly represents a real Gose. Not as sour & salty as I would have liked, but it is very refreshing on a hot summers night.
